---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /listen/index.html
title: "Listen"
seoTitle: "Listen — The Symbiotic Mind Podcast"
description: "Conversations on human-AI relationship design, behavioral science, and what it means to think alongside artificial intelligence. Hosted by Vlad Sterngold and Milena S. Nikolova, PhD."
---

{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "PodcastSeries",
  "name": {{ podcast.show.title | dump | safe }},
  "url": "{{ page.url | absUrl(site.url) }}",
  "description": {{ podcast.show.description | dump | safe }},
  "image": "{{ podcast.show.image | absUrl(site.url) }}",
  "inLanguage": "{{ podcast.show.language }}",
  "author": [
    {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Vlad Sterngold",
      "url": "{{ authors.vlad.url }}"
    },
    {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Milena S. Nikolova",
      "url": "{{ authors.milena.url }}"
    }
  ],
  "publisher": { "@id": "{{ site.url }}/#organization" },
  "webFeed": "{{ '/podcast.xml' | absUrl(site.url) }}"
}
</script>
{% set crumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Listen', url: page.url }
] %}
{% include "partials/breadcrumbs.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

<div class="about-header">
  <h1>Listen</h1>
  <p class="about-sub">The audio companion to The Symbiotic Mind. Long-form conversations between Vlad and Milena on the relationship design problem of AI × HI.</p>
</div>

<div class="about-body">
  <p>Subscribe in your podcast app of choice — the feed auto-distributes to Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Overcast, Pocket Casts, and every other major directory.</p>

  <p class="listen-subscribe">
    <a href="/podcast.xml" class="post-tag">RSS feed</a>
    <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/podcast/idTBD" class="post-tag">Apple Podcasts</a>
    <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/TBD" class="post-tag">Spotify</a>
    <a href="https://overcast.fm/itunes-TBD" class="post-tag">Overcast</a>
    <a href="https://pca.st/TBD" class="post-tag">Pocket Casts</a>
    <a href="{{ podcast.show.youtubeChannelUrl }}" class="post-tag">YouTube</a>
  </p>
</div>

{% if podcast.episodes.length %}
<ul class="post-list">
{% for ep in podcast.episodes %}
  <li>
    <div class="post-meta">{{ ep.pubDate | postDate }} &middot; Episode {{ ep.number }} &middot; {{ ep.duration }}</div>
    <h2><a href="/episodes/{{ ep.slug }}/">{{ ep.title }}</a></h2>
    <p class="post-excerpt">{{ ep.description }}</p>
    <audio controls preload="none" src="{{ ep.audio.url }}" style="width:100%; margin-top:0.75rem;"></audio>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<div class="about-body">
  <p><em>No episodes yet. Subscribe to the feed and the first episode will land directly in your podcast app the moment it ships.</em></p>
</div>
{% endif %}

{% include "partials/newsletter.njk" %}
